{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_04_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 最高の衣装デザイン",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2742073834
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、千紗\nこれからダンスレッスンか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Chisa.\nHeading to dance practice now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3910888154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、お姉ちゃんと二人で\n新ユニットの振り付けを練習するんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm practicing the choreography with my sister\nfor our new unit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9189031918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん、私とお姉ちゃんを\n新ユニットに選んでくれてありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san‚ thank you for choosing my sister\nand me for the new unit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5232542381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんとユニットを組めるなんて夢みたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like a dream to be in a unit with my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、沙季と組めるのが本当に嬉しいんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ you're really happy to be paired with Saki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい……だって、お姉ちゃんは私の憧れだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… after all‚ my sister is my idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "私が小さい頃、お姉ちゃんがアイドルの真似をして\n歌ってくれたことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was little‚ she used to imitate idols\nand sing for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4421081896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "その時のお姉ちゃんは凄くキラキラしていて……\n私もこんな風になりたいって思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She looked so shiny then…\nI've always wanted to be like her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6729479581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "それが、私がアイドルに憧れるようになった\nきっかけなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what inspired me\nto be an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7514270283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗はアイドルを目指す沙季を見て\n自分も追いかけてみたいと思ったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ seeing Saki aim to be an idol made you\nwant to follow in her footsteps.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7232439827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "はい……最近もお姉ちゃんの活躍を見て\nやっぱり凄いなあって思ってたので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Recently‚ seeing my sister's success‚\nI've been thinking how amazing she is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5958457924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "同じアイドルとして、目標だったお姉ちゃんと\n一緒に歌えるのが凄く嬉しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's really exciting to be able to sing together with my sister‚\nwho's been my idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7568368017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ちを大切にしてライブに臨んでくれ\n姉妹で息の合ったパフォーマンスを期待してるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Keep that feeling and bring it to the live performance.\nI'm looking forward to a perfectly synced performance from the sisters.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6136828922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\nお姉ちゃんの足を引っ張らないように頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nI'll do my best not to drag my sister down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7977155514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "足を引っ張らないようにか……\n千紗のそういうところは相変わらずだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not dragging her down‚ huh…\nThat's so like you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5247972111,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3701.1557519000035,
          "startTime": 89.3678224186
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗は少し沙季に頼り過ぎなところがあるな）\n（一皮むけるきっかけがあればいいんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Chisa relies a bit too much on Saki.）\n（If only she could find a way to grow one step further……）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6013294644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8133997599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！\n私が新ユニットの衣装を作るんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!?\nAm I going to make the outfits for the new team!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8009538482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いつもはデザイナーさん中心だが、今回は千紗が\nアイデアを出して二人の衣装をデザインしてほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Usually it's the designer's job‚ but this time I want Chisa\nto come up with ideas and design outfits for the two of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7296450025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "でも……私には荷が重過ぎます……\n自信ありません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… it's too much for me…\nI don't have confidence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5755832027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、これ以上の適任者はいないと思ってる\n想像してくれ、その衣装で二人がステージで歌う姿を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe there's no one more suitable for the job.\nImagine the two of you on stage wearing the outfits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1220783609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "私とお姉ちゃんが、私の考えた衣装を着て\nステージで歌う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister and I‚ wearing the outfits I designed‚\nsinging on stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2059586569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "それが出来たら素敵だと思いますけど……\n本当に私がデザインしていいんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be wonderful if we could do that‚ but…\nAre you sure I can design them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2199127916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺はぜひ千紗にやってほしい\n千紗はやってみたくないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really want you to do it‚ Chisa.\nDon't you want to give it a try?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2611453621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "……やってみたいです\nお姉ちゃんと私の衣装を作ってみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I want to give it a try.\nI want to make outfits for my sister and me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "千紗なら出来るさ\n二人に似合う最高の衣装をデザインしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can do it‚ Chisa.\nDesign the best outfits that suit both of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.047058737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました……お姉ちゃんがキラキラ輝けるような\n最高の衣装を作れるように頑張ります……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood… I'll do my best to create\nthe best outfits that make my sister shine…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.2818583865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（この衣装制作がうまくいって）\n（千紗の自信に繋がってくれるといいが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If this outfit-making goes well）\n（It might boost Chisa's confidence…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0687076649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A frew days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.2353927613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 177.3714248658
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 177.3714248658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……\nここのデザインはもっとこうした方がいいかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…\nShould I adjust this design a bit more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.2421839919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
